Package: summarizeandplot
Title: Summarize and Visualize Grouped Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Gelareh", "Modara", email = "gelarehmodara@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions to calculate and visualize summary statistics of grouped data.
    It includes features for calculating the mean and standard deviation of a numeric variable,
    grouping by a specified column, and returning both a summary table and a ggplot2-based plot with error bars.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
Imports:
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    stats
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
